4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science and Machine Learning bootcamp designed for beginners to start a career as a data scientist. The 16-week program includes three classes per week with a maximum of 12 students per class. Participants will learn Python, SQL, Statics, and tools like Pandas and Numpy to create predictive models and tackle real-life data challenges. Instructors include experienced professionals with PhDs in related fields. Certificates are recognized by multiple organizations, and the course is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop